long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A Chrome extension designed to streamline the process of autofilling out job application forms with given resume data for WorkUp users.

- Autofill job forms using your resume or make a master resume
- Includes ATS checks
- Preview Resumes
& More
